inutes on the app will make you exit it.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eGoogle\u0026#39;s Digital Wellbeing tools are available on Pixel smartphones and a variety of other Android devices, including those from OnePlus, Oppo, and Nothing. However, Samsung has its own suite of Digital Wellbeing tools, which do not yet include a \u0026#34;reminders\u0026#34; option. So unless you have a Samsung phone, you can expect this new reminder option to show up in your phone soon.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eSource: \u003ca href=\"https://9to5google.com/2024/11/18/google-screen-time-reminders-android-pixel/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e9to5Google\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e    \u003c/div\u003e\n    \n        \n\n    \n\n        \n\n\n                \n        \n        \n\n\n        \n\n\n\n\n\n                    \n        \n    \u003c/article\u003e\n\n    \n        \u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
